---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Overview
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        A short orientation what to expect in which of my feeds
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        A brief guide what you can expect behind the icons and links at the top of this page. This overview will get updated as needed.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-6">
        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="mdi:github" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                The programming sideprojects that I consider worthy are publicly available on my 
                <a href="https://github.com/PPetermeier" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  Github
                </a> 
                page where this pages is also hosted.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="mdi:twitter" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                I'm most active on
                <a href="https://x.com/infornomics" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  Twitter
                </a>,
                where I aggregate posts according to my outlined interests and occasionally engage with others, hopefully to the benefit of ourselves and others.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="mdi:linkedin" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/philipp-petermeier-6ba469229" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  LinkedIn
                </a>
                is mainly a professional networking platform and of a communication channel than a public space for me.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="simple-icons:substack" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                On my
                <a href="https://infornomics.substack.com/" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  Substack
                </a>
                you will find longer discussions on various topics that have been on my mind and needed to be put down in writing.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="mdi:email" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                You can
                <a href="mailto:p.petermeier@posteo.de" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  contact me directly
                </a>
                via my email address.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="text-primary-600 mt-1">
              <Icon name="mdi:file-document" size={24} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                My 
                <a href="/uploads/CV_for_Website.pdf" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  CV
                </a> 
                without private information can be downloaded from the last icon, if the 
                <a href="/skills" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-semibold">
                  Education & Skills
                </a> 
                leaves you wanting something more formal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>